answers.body_markdown:
You need to override `onNewIntent` in your `MainActivity` class.

     @Override
     protected void onNewIntent(Intent intent){
          super.onNewIntent(intent);
          // write your open notification fragment code here
     }

When push notification is tapped, it will call `onNewIntent`. Write all your logic in `onNewIntent`.

